node.title: Simone Biles is engaged to Jonathan Owens
node.description: Simone Biles revealed she "woke up a fiance√©," sharing photos of Owens' proposal.
node.content: ["Olympian and gymnastics \"GOAT\" Simone Biles just added fiance\u00e9 to her list of titles. The 24-year-old posted Tuesday on Twitter that she \"woke up a fiance\u00e9,\" sharing photos from her engagement to Jonathan Owens.", "\"I can't wait to spend forever & ever with you, you're everything I dreamed of and more! let's get married!\" she tweeted. The photos show a shocked Biles as Owens gets down on one knee inside a gazebo.\u00a0", "The pair got engaged in Houston, Texas, where Biles grew up and Owens, who is in the NFL, plays for the Houston Texans.", "WOKE UP A FIANC\u00c9E \ud83d\udc8d\ud83d\udc8d\ud83d\ude2d", "I can\u2019t wait to spend forever & ever with you, you\u2019re everything I dreamed of and more! let\u2019s get married!  \ud83d\udd4a\ud83e\udd0e@jjowens_3 pic.twitter.com/BcrWvhEE38", "The athletes began dating in 2020. Both posted about the engagement on Instagram, with Biles saying it was \"the easiest yes.\"", "The two celebrated their first anniversary while Biles was competing at the Olympics in Tokyo, and couldn't be together due to COVID-19 restrictions.\u00a0", "Biles pulled out of several Olympic events for mental health reasons, and Owens posted about\u00a0her \"strength and courage\" on Instagram, saying she inspires him more and more every day.", "Caitlin O'Kane is a digital content producer covering trending stories for CBS News and its good news brand, The Uplift."]
